<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mt-3">FAQs</h1>

<div class="container mx-auto mt-8 p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">What is E-Greetings Send Cards?</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        E-Greetings Send Cards is an innovative online platform designed to help users create and send personalized electronic cards, commonly known as E-cards, to friends and family. This service allows you to express your feelings and share special moments through beautifully designed digital cards that can be customized for any occasion. You can browse a wide selection of templates categorized under various themes, ensuring that there’s something perfect for every celebration. Whether it's a birthday, anniversary, holiday, or just a simple greeting, E-Greetings makes it easy to connect with loved ones from anywhere in the world, all while adding a personal touch to your messages.
    </p>
    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">How do I create and send an e-card?</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        To create and send an E-card using E-Greetings, begin by visiting our website at <a href="https://egreetingstest.azurewebsites.net/">https://egreetingstest.azurewebsites.net/</a> . Once there, explore the various categories under "E-cards," "Special," or view the featured E-cards displayed on the homepage. After selecting a card that resonates with you, choose between portrait or landscape orientation to access the E-card design page. Utilize our user-friendly editing tools to personalize the card, adding your own text, images, and even videos to make your message unique. Once you are satisfied with your design, click "Save" to move on to the next step, where you can input recipient email addresses, set the desired sending date and time, and add any multimedia elements. Finally, proceed to payment to complete your order and send your heartfelt E-card.
    </p>
    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">Is there a cost to use E-Greetings Send Cards?</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        Yes, using E-Greetings Send Cards involves certain costs. Each card you send to a recipient's email address is priced at $2, in addition to any fees associated with the specific card template you choose. While many templates are available for free, some premium designs may incur additional charges. It’s important to review the pricing details of each card before finalizing your selection. This pricing structure allows us to maintain high-quality designs and continuous improvement of our services. Additionally, you can explore special offers or subscription plans that may provide more value if you plan to send multiple cards.
    </p>

    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">
        Do I need to create an account to use the service?
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        Creating an account is a requirement for using E-Greetings Send Cards. Before you can design and send your E-cards, you must log in or sign up for a new account. This process ensures that your personalized designs, messages, and recipient information are securely stored and easily accessible for future use. Registering for an account also allows you to manage your orders, track your sent cards, and receive updates and promotional offers tailored to your preferences. This added layer of security and convenience is designed to enhance your overall experience on our platform.
    </p>

    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">Can I upload my own photos or designs for an e-card?</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        Absolutely! E-Greetings encourages creativity and personalization, allowing you to upload your own photos or designs when creating an E-card. This feature enables you to transform your card into a unique keepsake that reflects your personal style and the sentiment you wish to convey. Simply use the upload function in the design tool to add your images, whether they are cherished family photos, custom graphics, or any visuals that enhance your message. This capability not only adds a personal touch but also makes your E-card stand out as a memorable gift for your recipients.
    </p>

    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">Personalization Design</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        The personalization design feature at E-Greetings allows you to create E-cards that truly reflect your personality and style. With user-friendly editing tools, you can modify text, colors, fonts, and layouts to match the theme of your card and the occasion you are celebrating. The platform also supports multimedia elements, enabling you to add videos and images that resonate with your message. By using these customization options, you can craft a heartfelt E-card that captures your emotions and connects with the recipient on a deeper level. The flexibility to personalize every aspect of your card ensures that your message is not only seen but also felt.
    </p>

    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">Payment and Pricing</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        At E-Greetings, we offer a seamless payment process to ensure your experience is convenient and secure. You can make payments using popular methods such as PayPal or MoMo, giving you flexibility in how you choose to complete your transactions. After you finalize your order, you can easily track your purchases in the "Order" section of your account. Additionally, after your E-card is successfully sent, you have the opportunity to provide feedback on your order within three days, helping us continuously improve our services. Our pricing structure is designed to be transparent, so you will always know what you’re paying for, including any additional fees for premium card templates.
    </p>
    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">
        How to use Sub plan?
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        E-Greetings offers three subscription plans: Basic, Standard, and Premium, designed to cater to different needs and sending frequencies. After purchasing a subscription, your account will be activated by our admin page, enabling you to send cards for a period of 30 days. Each day, you can send one card simultaneously to 10, 15, or 20 emails, depending on the subscription level you choose. Each plan allows you to design up to three card templates, ensuring that you have enough variety for your recipients. Additionally, we offer combo send packages, where you can buy 10, 15, or 20 sends at once, providing better value for frequent users. This structured approach to subscriptions allows you to manage your E-card sending effectively while enjoying cost savings.
    </p>
    <h2 class=" text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #0F2F76; font-weight: 700">
        Are my messages and photos secure?
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
        Yes, E-Greetings prioritizes your privacy and security. All messages and photos you upload are securely stored, ensuring that your personal information remains confidential. We implement robust security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or breaches. Additionally, our platform ensures that your designs and messages are encrypted during transmission, providing peace of mind as you share your sentiments with loved ones. We are committed to maintaining a safe environment for all users, so you can focus on creating and sending your heartfelt E-cards without worry. If you have any concerns about security, our support team is always available to assist you.

        For further inquiries, please feel free to reach out to our support team. Enjoy using E-Greetings to send your personalized E-cards!
    </p>
